latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The secret is no more secret now 🤭

Vedix is India’s 1st customized Ayurveda. 

Its being 4 months I am using this products which is truely according to my hair type and concerns and I am so happy with the results and that you also can see 😉

All products they make are free from harmful chemical like SLS, paraben and Sulphate. 

My three steps hair care routine - 

🎀 Shampoo - This Dandruff control shampoo is rich with antifungal, anti bacterial & anti inflammatory properties clears dandruff by gently cleansing away dead skin cells and dirt. 

🎀 Oil - I gently massage with it for 10-15min and leave it over night. Its very nourishing and helped me with hair growth too. 

🎀 Serum - I apply 3-5ml of serum over my dry hair. Gently massage for 5-10min. It gives my hair a nice texture and stimulate hair growth. 

Just take a quick hair quiz to know about your hair and doshas. They will customize the product according to you so that you can get the best results. 

Check their website to know more @vedixofficial 

.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Edited by - @krishna_pictures_photography_ 
Welcome to my IGTV
1- Take 2spoon of gram flour (besan)
2- Add raw milk/curd
3- Add honey and turmeric
4- Few drops of lemon
5- Add a little rice flour
Mix all this together and apply gently all over the face, do it twice a week for better results. It is helpful to reduce tanning,dead skin and gives you a ultimate glow.

Udaipur mein folk dance toh bahut jagah hota hai par Virasat jaise performance mene kahin nahi dekha.
Jab main inhe perform karte dekh rahi thi — expressions, energy, rhythm sab on point tha Performance ke beech mujhe literally goosebumps aa gaye.
Aur sabse inspiring baat?
Yahan na jise folk dance sikhna pasand he vo aake free mein seekh sakta hai.
So next time jab Udaipur aao, yaad rakhna –
📍Virasat at Hathi Than Haveli is not just a show, it’s a soul-stirring experience.

latestPosts.caption:
🌊 HONEST REVIEW: Found Dubai’s hidden gem for families!
Guys, I was skeptical when I heard about a family-friendly beach club in Dubai (most are 21+ only), but Riva Beach Club on Palm Jumeirah completely won me over! 🙌
What actually impressed me:
The food was genuinely delicious - not your typical overpriced beach club fare. Their grilled seafood and fresh salads were chef’s kiss 👨‍🍳✨
Kids had their own pool (finally!) while adults got the heated pool with actual good vibes. The cabanas felt private without being stuffy, and the service? Incredibly warm and attentive.

Real talk: This place gets busy on weekends, so book ahead. But honestly? Worth every dirham for an stress-free family beach day.

[Beach club in Dubai, palm jumeirah, Dubai with kids, family beach club in Dubai ]
